column1: Today we celebrate #NationalNursesDay and #GA12 nurses for the incredible work they are doing on the front lines battling COVID-19. #ThankYouNurses for being our heroes and caring for our loved ones when they need it the most. https://t.co/WdinTI4Huq

Today we celebrate #WorldHealthDay & the work of nurses & midwives & the critical role they play in keeping the world healthy. We also honor all our medical personnel on the front lines & for everyone doing their part to help slow the spread of COVID-19. #SupportNursesAndMidwives https://t.co/8bAd7Ui7Kw

8PM tonight @GovKemp's live town hall on GA's response to the spread of #COVID19 & what GA is doing to combat it. Along w/ ATL Mayor @KeishaBottoms @GaDPH Com Dr Kathleen Toomey @GeorgiaEMA Dir Homer Bryson & @GA_DOI Com John King. Aired on most local news & @mygpb stations. https://t.co/jzIECOcXKV

Let's support our local restaurants today & participate in the #GreatAmericanTakeoutDay! The restaurant industry is struggling with the COVID-19 but we can help by ordering take out or using a delivery service tonight & support our community. #WeAreInThisTogether https://t.co/kIMxqW06ZA
